	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator. A calamitosus whom Mark Antony restored in 49, so probably a senator (Cic. Phil. 2.56, with the reading Denticula in some mss; Dio 45.47.1 #). (TJC) See Shackleton Bailey, Studies 47.\n" .
